y+z=1
4x^2+4(y-0.5)^2=1
S
(x,y,z)=G(u,v)
\displaystyle \frac{dG}{du}\times \frac{dG}{dv}
 x = u/2 \cos(v) , y = 1/2 + u/2 \sin(v) ,  z = 1/2 - u/2 \sin(v)
 v =[0,2\pi)
 u = [0,1]
